Available Tools: get_sensor_reading | get_all_sensors | get_sensor_by_location | get_sensor_battery
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "sensor_id": "string", "location": "string", "type": "temperature|humidity|motion|co2|light" }
Response Schema: { "sensor_id": "string", "type": "string", "value": number, "unit": "string", "timestamp": "string", "battery_pct": number }
---
Question: What is the CO2 concentration in the conference room?
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_by_location", "sensor_id": "", "location": "Conference Room B", "type": "co2" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "CR-CO2-03", "type": "co2", "value": 412.5, "unit": "ppm", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:00:00Z", "battery_pct": 89 }

Question: Check the light intensity in the parking garage.
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_by_location", "sensor_id": "", "location": "Parking Garage Level 2", "type": "light" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "PG-LGT-09", "type": "light", "value": 150.0, "unit": "Lux", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T15:00:05Z", "battery_pct": 94 }

Question: Get the reading from sensor ID MOT-ENT-01.
Call: { "func_call": "get_sensor_reading", "sensor_id": "MOT-ENT-01", "location": "", "type": "motion" }
Response: { "sensor_id": "MOT-ENT-01", "type": "motion", "value": 1.0, "unit": "Boolean", "timestamp": "2023-10-27T14:59:55Z", "battery_pct": 42 }

